name: Smart Glass Analytical Dashboard UI
description:
Hey Everyone!

Here is my dashboard exploration.

I tried to make a digital wellbeing dashboard where we can track how much we spend our daily time, whether it's on a laptop, mobile, or just walking to the Starbucks for a coffee break. This dashboard helps to make a balance between digital and real life.

 I hope you enjoy it. Please give us a thumbs up and leave a remark.
